Class VolumeSetPDS3

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nasa.arc.pds.xml.generated.VolumeSetPDS3
  • public class VolumeSetPDS3
extends java.lang.Object
    The Volume_Set_PDS3 class is used to capture the volume set information from the PDS3 Data Set Catalog.
